{"tid":1347940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖=李蓮英；黑警社團=東西廠，都要對付","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:33:07.000Z","uid":120623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"338273dc2d56b8617bba14aa6fcbd37a0b8777b5","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"雖然之前係咁出po講要對準政權對準中聯辦，但琴晚元朗單野已經唔係單純地區既人民鬥人民，而係單方面既無差別恐怖襲擊，係中央要嚇退大家既卑劣手段。<br />\n<br />\n今日已經講到對家吹晒雞有晒架生，要大家唔好出現係元天屯，咁係咩？黑社會接掌執法角色同執行戒嚴，見人就打見人就扑見人就斬，你喺條街存在已經係被佢地施暴既理由。<br />\n<br />\n全城白色恐怖，會增加好多市民上街既成本：唔係唔想出，但係唔敢再出，因為人身安全受到直接威脅同恐嚇。所以要先指向何妖，迅速解決臨危之急，先可以清除障礙，直指政權。當然，身為助攻無視暴行既黑警我地都唔可以放過，仲要佢地喺上環又瘋狂開槍爆人頭，沒有一個是無辜！"},{"pid":"e518f9f0905e271fb8f1718e40aaedab3316d395","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"一個二個都係閹人黎！"},{"pid":"0774379b0e96aad3a0fde1cc475696280af673ff","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e644943af17e7a0fb8942aa575f964df356dd9","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447b2d8fe83f6c019d6979daa091a0152904ac4d","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b7f26ddfea9a223812f45c59b4b498fcba1fe6","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac21bf100b020cd705052e04bb4244fec4abe46","tid":1347940,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gi